---
title: Creamy Harissa King Prawn Spaghetti with Spinach and Cheese
description: Looking for a super quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Creamy Harissa King Prawn Spaghetti in just 15 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R07_W30_UK_UQ22111-3_MME_MAIN_low-6eb18cb0.jpg
